two of his ribs

430
00:19:19,252 --> 00:19:21,870
to create the anterior
and posterior larynx frame

431
00:19:21,954 --> 00:19:24,340
and then stretch
the cartilage across it.

432
00:19:24,424 --> 00:19:27,243
