454
00:20:19,942 --> 00:20:21,960
It we wait any longer,
he may not be able

455
00:20:22,045 --> 00:20:23,797
to learn to speak,
even with a larynx.

456
00:20:23,882 --> 00:20:25,580
He can communicate
without speaking.

457
00:20:27,674 --> 00:20:29,058
You're making
a big mistake.

458
00:20:29,143 --> 00:20:30,205
(SIGHS) Murphy.

459
00:20:30,290 --> 00:20:33,376
He'll always be...
Limited.

460
00:20:33,900 --> 00:20:35,861
