00:21:00,274 --> 00:21:01,791
The suture repair
looks fine.

467
00:21:01,985 --> 00:21:04,377
Which makes me think
the nerve here got compressed

468
00:21:04,462 --> 00:21:06,280
between the bone
and the dog's teeth.

469
00:21:06,364 --> 00:21:08,616
