the severed nerve ends

473
00:21:14,005 --> 00:21:15,001
to grow
toward each other,

474
00:21:15,086 --> 00:21:16,814
create a pathway for them
to connect and heal.

475
00:21:16,898 --> 00:21:19,283
I'm not sure the nerves
can grow across that distance.

